column1: #text=After a couple days from ordering the plane tickets online .
#text=I drove over to the airport which took about 45 minutes .
#text=Upon arriving there I parked my car and walked inside the airport .
#text=I had to go through security first which checked everything , and I walked to find the wing where my assigned airplane was at .
#text=Once I found it , I drop off my luggage and go to the clerk with my plane ticket .
#text=After she inspects it , I go on the airplane and sit onto my assigned seat .
#text=Since this was my first ride , I decided to not sit near the window in order to prevent getting sick .
#text=After the plane filled up with more people , we ended up taking off .
#text=During the ride everyone was very quite and there was a movie playing during the ride .
#text=After 2 hours the plane arrived to the next airport and I got off .
#text=I picked up my luggage , and met up with my friend who met me there .
